1. Jupiter's latest aggregator Juno is now online;
2. Bitcoin has achieved a new high in market value, but short-term Bitcoin holders are still in a loss-making state, and risk aversion dominates the market;
3. Walrus will issue airdrops to holders of SUI ecological game console SuiPlay0X1;
4. Virtuals launched the points-based new issuance mechanism Genesis, and the first new issuance project is h011yw00d (HOLLY);
5. Magic Eden: The first quarter airdrop has been completed, and the second quarter activity has started;
6. LINK's market value exceeds the New York Times, reaching 8.25 billion US dollars;
7. The founder of Synthetix changed his personal X username to kain.depeg (de-anchoring);
8. ARK Invest reduced its holdings of Bitcoin ETF by $3.35 million on the 17th and increased its holdings of Solana ETF by $4.95 million.
